name: integer_i32_maximum
description: |
  This is the maximum i32 value, 2147483647. Adding 1 produces the
  unrepresentable value 2147483648 and may trap, wrap to -2147483648, saturate,
  or be evaluated in a wider type. The same bit pattern is the last u32
  value that converts to i32 without changing the mathematical value.
format: hex
decode-as: i32
pair:
  - with: one.input
    hint: tricky
  - with: ../u32/signed-maximum.input
    hint: tricky
tags:
  - "integer"
  - "signed-integer"
  - "i32"
  - "maximum"
  - "boundary"
  - "overflow"
  - "conversion"
  - "two's-complement"
---
ff ff ff 7f # 2147483647
